<section class="container page-shell">
  <h1 class="section-title">Frequently Asked Questions</h1>
  <p class="section-subtitle">Answers to the most common questions about memberships and class booking.</p>
  <div class="accordion card p-2" id="faq">
    <div class="accordion-item"><h2 class="accordion-header"><button class="accordion-button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#q1">Can I pause my membership?</button></h2><div id="q1" class="accordion-collapse collapse show" data-bs-parent="#faq"><div class="accordion-body">This demo system supports renew and cancel flows. Pause can be added as a future enhancement.</div></div></div>
    <div class="accordion-item"><h2 class="accordion-header"><button class="accordion-button collapsed" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#q2">Do I need to book classes in advance?</button></h2><div id="q2" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#faq"><div class="accordion-body">Yes. Members reserve slots from the bookings dashboard. If a class is full, they can join the waitlist.</div></div></div>
    <div class="accordion-item"><h2 class="accordion-header"><button class="accordion-button collapsed" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#q3">Can beginners join?</button></h2><div id="q3" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#faq"><div class="accordion-body">Absolutely. Programs are structured for all levels, with coaches who can guide first-time members.</div></div></div>
  </div>
</section>
